'''血小板无力症''' 是一种极其罕见的血液疾病，原因是[[血小板|血小板]]缺乏[[糖蛋白|糖蛋白]]IIb/IIIa受体(GPIIB/IIIA), 所以[[纤维蛋白原|纤维蛋白原]]很难[[交联|交联]]，致使[[出血|出血]]时间显著延长。

==[[病理生理学|病理生理学]]==

==病因学==
血小板无力症屬自體隱性遺傳<ref name=seligsohn>Seligsohn U. Glanzmann thrombasthenia: a model disease which paved the way to powerful therapeutic agents. Pathophysiol Haemost Thromb. 2002 Sep-Dec;32(5-6):216-7. PMID 13679645. [http://content.karger.com/ProdukteDB/produkte.asp?Aktion=ShowPDF&ArtikelNr=73569&ProduktNr=224034&Ausgabe=229381&filename=73569.pdf Free Full Text] {{Wayback|url=http://content.karger.com/ProdukteDB/produkte.asp?Aktion=ShowPDF&ArtikelNr=73569&ProduktNr=224034&Ausgabe=229381&filename=73569.pdf |date=20110516214314 }}.</ref>，另亦可由[[自體免疫性疾病|自體免疫性疾病]]引致<ref>Tholouli E, Hay CR, O'Gorman P, Makris M. Acquired Glanzmann's thrombasthenia without thrombocytopenia: a severe acquired autoimmune bleeding disorder. Br J Haematol. 2004 Oct;127(2):209-13. PMID 15461628.</ref>。

